  <h4>Waterproof?</h4>
    <p> Jewelbots are water-resistant, but not waterproof.  That means it's okay if they get slightly wet, but they should not be worn in the shower or pool!
  <h4>Cleaning your Jewelbots</h4>
    <p>If you want to clean your Jewelbot, remove the charm and band from the hardware piece, and soak in warm water and dish soap, then scrub it gently with a soft brush or towel.</p>

